This paper discusses extensions to SPARQL, the standard query language for RDF graphs, to allow for querying with respect to RDF schemas and ontologies. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including databases (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), software engineering (cs.SE), and digital libraries (cs.DL).
